 826:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *        returned) to convert SubSeconds value in second fraction ratio with
 827:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *        time unit following generic formula:
 828:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *        Second fraction ratio * time_unit =
 829:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           [(SecondFraction - SubSeconds) / (SecondFraction + 1)] * time_unit
