1693:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         synchronized with RTC APB clock.
1694:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   * @note   The RTC Resynchronization mode is write protected, use the
1695:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         __HAL_RTC_WRITEPROTECTION_DISABLE() before calling this function.
