1697:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         initialization, calendar update or after wakeup from low power modes
1698:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         the software must first clear the RSF flag.
1699:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         The software must then wait until it is set again before reading
1700:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         the calendar, which means that the calendar registers have been
1701:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         correctly copied into the RTC_TR and RTC_DR shadow registers.
